### Global ###
# Propagate message deletion
Expunge Both

# Automatically create missing mailboxes, both locally and on the server
Create Both

# Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *

### MUHQ ###

IMAPAccount MUHQ
Host euporie.uberspace.de
User muhq@muhq.space
PassCmd "pass email/MUHQ"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore MUHQ-remote
Account MUHQ

MaildirStore MUHQ-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/maildir/MUHQ/
Inbox ~/.local/share/maildir/MUHQ/INBOX

Channel MUHQ
Far :MUHQ-remote:
Near :MUHQ-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *

